testsuite.name: com.example.services.FactServiceTest

testcase.name: getAllFacts should return all facts from the repository()
getOriginalPermalink should return null if permalink does not exist()
getOriginalPermalink should retrieve a permalink and increment access count()
fetchAndShortenFacts should fetch a fact and store it in the repository()
getFact should retrieve a fact and increment access count()
getAccessStatistics should return statistics from the repository()
getFact should return null if fact does not exist()
